title: Counter-Strike Source - v1.0 - 08.04.2013 [WTF] [Non-Steam] [Onl
description:
This is the WTF release of Counter-Strike Source. This version is up to date as of 8/4/2013.

The release includes:
* Working Favorites/History
* Working Achievements
* Built-In Non-Steam Server List
* Clean release, no additional extras. As close to the retail game as possible.

If you have problems, please make sure DirectX and VCRedist are installed, please make sure UAC is disabled and you run the game as administrator. 

Questions? Leave them in the comments.
